A11y Dialog
a11y-dialog is a lightweight (1.3Kb) yet flexible script to create accessible dialog windows.
✔︎ No dependencies✔︎ Leveraging the native  element✔︎ Closing dialog on overlay click and ESC✔︎ Toggling aria-* attributes✔︎ Trapping and restoring focus✔︎ Firing events✔︎ DOM and JS APIs✔︎ Fast and tiny  
You can try the live demo ↗.
